The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Wayne Cannie, Appellant. [864 NYS2d 378]

Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County (Bruce Allen, J.), rendered on or about November 29, 2007, unanimously affirmed. No opinion. Order filed. Concur—Saxe, J.P., Sweeny, McGuire, Renwick and Freedman, JJ.
